WaniKani_Meaning_Mnemonic: The commander's alcohol is really just soy sauce. When he goes out to drink with his troops and they all get drunk together, he manages to have fun and stay sober by drinking down a tasty, non-alcoholic pint of soy sauce.
WaniKani_Meaning_Info: The next time you go to a bar, order yourself a commander's alcohol. It's like saying you want a Roy Rogers or a Shirley Temple, except it isn't pretty and it tastes horrible.
WaniKani_Reading_Mnemonic: Soy sauce also happens to be the Shougun's (しょう) favorite drink. Unfortunately, he can't just tell people he likes drinking glasses of soy sauce, or they'll look at him weird. Instead he orders it as a commander's alcohol too.
WaniKani_Reading_Info: Picture the Shougun sitting on his throne, guzzling down some salty, brown soy sauce. It's splashing on his robes and the smell is making his assistants gag.
Kanshudo_mnemonic: the commander's (将) sake flask (酉) has soy sauce in it

(2)用麦、面、豆等发酵制成的调味品。
(3)将鱼、肉、蔬、果捣烂制成的糊状食品。
(4)泛指糊状物。
(5)用酱或酱油腌制、浸渍。
(6)搅混；沾染。

(2) Condiments made from the fermentation of wheat, noodles, beans, etc.
(3) A mashed food made by mashing fish, meat, vegetables, and fruits.
(4) Generally refers to paste.
(5) Pickled and dipped in sauce or soy sauce.
(6) Stirring; contaminating.

Radicals: 将, 酉  (commander, alcohol)
Meaning Mnemonic
The commander's alcohol is really just soy sauce. When he goes out to drink with his troops and they all get drunk together, he manages to have fun and stay sober by drinking down a tasty, non-alcoholic pint of soy sauce.
The next time you go to a bar, order yourself a commander's alcohol. It's like saying you want a Roy Rogers or a Shirley Temple, except it isn't pretty and it tastes horrible.
Reading Mnemonic
Soy sauce also happens to be the Shougun's (しょう) favorite drink. Unfortunately, he can't just tell people he likes drinking glasses of soy sauce, or they'll look at him weird. Instead he orders it as a commander's alcohol too.
Picture the Shougun sitting on his throne, guzzling down some salty, brown soy sauce. It's splashing on his robes and the smell is making his assistants gag.
